Zhai Qiuyu's master.

290
00:21:52,599 --> 00:21:53,799
He's preparing a special set of tactics

291
00:21:53,799 --> 00:21:55,200
specifically for Zhai Qiuyu.

292
00:21:55,720 --> 00:21:56,519
Master?

293
00:21:57,960 --> 00:21:59,119
This is quite urgent.

294
00:21:59,119 --> 00:22:00,599
Zhai Qiuyu's been worried for days.

295
00:22:02,039 --> 00:22:03,599
Is he going back too?

296
00:22:05,200 --> 00:22:06,519
Didn't Zhai Qiuyu tell you?

297
00:22:16,000 --> 00:22:17,200
I haven't told him yet.

298
00:22:20,519 --> 00:22:22,119
And you don't want to take him back.

299
00:22:22,119 --> 00:22:23,119
Of course I do.

300
00:22:24,200 --> 00:22:25,119
But I promised him

301
00:22:26,480 --> 00:22:27,519
unless he's willing

302
00:22:27,759 --> 00:22:28,839
I won't force him.

303
00:22:30,000 --> 00:22:31,839
Your Team Doctor position is still open.

304
00:22:32,200 --> 00:22:33,000
If he doesn't come back,

305
00:22:33,359 --> 00:22:34,200
who will do the job?

306
00:22:34,359 --> 00:22:35,559
Then just hire someone else.

307
00:22:36,720 --> 00:22:38,039
The Team Doctor is the Team Doctor,

308
00:22:40,039 --> 00:22:41,359
Li Youen is Li Youen.

309
00:22:41,880 --> 00:22:42,960
Don't mix them up.

310
00:22:44,559 --> 00:22:45,200
Right.

311
00:22:45,559 --> 00:22:47,559
When did your mindset become so noble?

312
00:22:50,359 --> 00:22:51,160
There are fish.

313
00:22:55,720 --> 00:22:56,680
What are you waiting for?

314
00:22:56,680 --> 00:22:57,440
Hurry up and catch it!

315
00:23:00,799 --> 00:23:02,119
Do you remember when we were kids?

316
00:23:02,400 --> 00:23:03,759
That big koi in the pond?

317
00:23:04,279 --> 00:23:05,400
The one I overfed to death?

318
00:23:07,200 --> 00:23:08,640
You secretly disposed of it later.

319
00:23:08,640 --> 00:23:09,920
And you insisted you ate it yourself.

320
00:23:10,200 --> 00:23:11,279
I took the blame for nothing.

321
00:23:11,359 --> 00:23:12,880
I wish I had actually eaten it.

322
00:23:13,079 --> 00:23:14,319
That fish was worth over 300,000 yuan.

323
00:23:17,119 --> 00:23:17,519
Quick!

324
00:23:17,519 --> 00:23:18,160
There, there!

325
00:23:35,519 --> 00:23:36,559
I can't anymore

326
00:23:36,839 --> 00:23:37,720
I'm starving to death

327
00:23:38,799 --> 00:23:39,960
It'll be soon

328
00:23:40,079 --> 00:23:41,000
It'll be soon

329
00:23:41,400 --> 00:23:42,480
I can't wait

330
00:23:42,880 --> 00:23:44,000
Let me take a bite of you first

331
00:23:44,240 --> 00:23:45,079
To fill my stomach

332
00:23:52,799 --> 00:23:54,599
Are you treating me like I'm not human?

333
00:23:57,880 --> 00:23:58,839
He's not

334
00:23:59,440 --> 00:24:00,200
He's jealous

335
00:24:03,599 --> 00:24:05,480
Your elbow can't take this kind of abuse

336
00:24:09,119 --> 00:24:10,640
Fighting with fish is something

337
00:24:11,039 --> 00:24:11,960
you shouldn't do again.

338
00:24:13,559 --> 00:24:14,279
Okay.

339
00:24:35,079 --> 00:24:36,160
I never asked you,

340
00:24:37,440 --> 00:24:39,920
how was this place fixed?

341
00:24:41,599 --> 00:24:42,599
My master did it.

342
00:24:43,240 --> 00:24:44,000
Ren Guodong.

343
00:24:44,880 --> 00:24:45,799
How did you know?

344
00:24:48,519 --> 00:24:49,720
Gu Hao told me.

345
00:24:51,440 --> 00:24:53,079
He said you were going back.

346
00:24:56,279 --> 00:24:57,559
Ask if I want to go together

347
00:24:58,240 --> 00:24:58,960
It wasn't me

348
00:24:59,240 --> 00:25:00,200
I didn't let him speak

349
00:25:00,440 --> 00:25:01,680
I told him to come explain to you

350
00:25:02,480 --> 00:25:03,200
Sit down

351
00:25:04,519 --> 00:25:05,440
It's not over yet

352
00:25:06,799 --> 00:25:07,559
Youen

353
00:25:08,279 --> 00:25:09,200
I don't want to press it anymore

354
00:25:12,839 --> 00:25:13,519
I

355
00:25:22,480 --> 00:25:23,160
I

356
00:25:41,559 --> 00:25:43,400
The fishing village isn't far from the club.

357
00:25:44,079 --> 00:25:45,480
I can go back and forth in a day.

358
00:25:49,160 --> 00:25:51,160
Didn't you want me to have days off every month?

359
00:25:51,720 --> 00:25:54,039
I'll come see you every day off from now on.

360
00:25:54,519 --> 00:25:55,240
Okay?

361
00:26:03,359 --> 00:26:04,079
Brother,

362
00:26:04,279 --> 00:26:05,559
I don't know how to cook fish.

363
00:26:08,799 --> 00:26:09,359
I...

364
00:26:09,359 --> 00:26:10,599
I'm going out first.

365
00:26:11,720 --> 00:26:12,960
You haven't answered me yet.

366
00:26:13,880 --> 00:26:14,759
Okay?

367
00:26:23,000 --> 00:26:23,480
Okay.

368
00:26:37,440 --> 00:26:38,200
I want that one.

369
00:26:38,200 --> 00:26:38,839
Okay.

370
00:26:41,720 --> 00:26:42,279
That one.

371
00:26:48,720 --> 00:26:50,119
You just spoil him.

372
00:26:50,759 --> 00:26:51,920
You don't have to be envious.

373
00:26:52,359 --> 00:26:53,319
Someone spoils you too.

374
00:27:00,559 --> 00:27:02,119
I don't know if it's cooked yet.

375
00:27:02,119 --> 00:27:03,200
Just take them all out.

376
00:27:04,000 --> 00:27:05,440
Don't try to poison my brother.

377
00:27:05,960 --> 00:27:08,279
If you're going to poison someone, it'll be me first.

378
00:27:15,079 --> 00:27:15,559
Here.

379
00:27:15,559 --> 00:27:16,160
Eat the fish.

380
00:27:27,279 --> 00:27:27,880
Stop

381
00:27:35,119 --> 00:27:36,920
We haven't gotten together in so long

382
00:27:39,240 --> 00:27:40,400
Now that we're finally together

383
00:27:41,759 --> 00:27:42,880
We have to part again tomorrow

384
00:27:49,599 --> 00:27:51,119
Then let's say some parting words

385
00:27:51,279 --> 00:27:51,960
What should we say?

386
00:27:52,839 --> 00:27:55,640
Say you three partners tricked me

387
00:27:56,480 --> 00:27:57,839
We had no choice

388
00:27:59,920 --> 00:28:01,559
If we must say parting words

389
00:28:06,039 --> 00:28:07,079
Then see you next time

390
00:28:08,079 --> 00:28:09,079
See you next time

391
00:28:18,720 --> 00:28:19,480
Let's eat

392
00:29:45,759 --> 00:29:46,480
Hello?

393
00:29:46,480 --> 00:29:47,279
Li Youen

394
00:29:48,279 --> 00:29:49,720
I haven't seen you in so long

395
00:29:50,920 --> 00:29:52,519
You've only been back for two days

396
00:29:52,799 --> 00:29:54,000
Only two days?

397
00:29:54,799 --> 00:29:56,119
How does it feel like so long?

398
00:29:57,880 --> 00:29:58,640
Youen

399
00:29:59,519 --> 00:30:00,480
I miss you

400
00:30:01,319 --> 00:30:02,599
How's your injury?

401
00:30:03,400 --> 00:30:04,640
Did they find the Team Doctor?

402
00:30:06,160 --> 00:30:06,960
I don't know

403
00:30:06,960 --> 00:30:08,319
where they recruited these misfits from.

404
00:30:08,519 --> 00:30:09,440
None of them are any good.

405
00:30:12,720 --> 00:30:13,960
Why aren't you talking?

406
00:30:14,880 --> 00:30:16,160
I didn't mean for you to come back.

407
00:30:16,160 --> 00:30:16,720
I...

408
00:30:17,200 --> 00:30:18,799
Didn't you ask me to?

409
00:30:19,000 --> 00:30:19,680
Brother,

410
00:30:20,920 --> 00:30:21,680
Xiao Si is here.

411
00:30:21,680 --> 00:30:22,519
I'll hang up now.

412
00:30:27,200 --> 00:30:28,200
Where's Zhai Qiuyu?

413
00:30:28,599 --> 00:30:30,119
I haven't seen him for two days.

414
00:30:30,119 --> 00:30:31,720
Don't you dislike him?

415
00:30:31,720 --> 00:30:32,640
Why are you still looking for him?

416
00:30:32,640 --> 00:30:34,680
Why wouldn't I like a free employee?

417
00:30:35,839 --> 00:30:36,799
Actually, bro,

418
00:30:37,319 --> 00:30:38,759
if you like him,

419
00:30:38,759 --> 00:30:39,480
then I like him.

420
00:30:41,279 --> 00:30:42,400
But he's gone.

421
00:30:42,400 --> 00:30:43,319
He went back to the club.

422
00:30:46,160 --> 00:30:47,200
It's good he left

423
00:30:47,359 --> 00:30:48,839
So he doesn't have to stay here

424
00:30:48,839 --> 00:30:49,720
eating so much

425
00:30:50,119 --> 00:30:51,200
and making you angry

426
00:30:54,519 --> 00:30:55,400
That's true

427
00:30:56,039 --> 00:30:56,839
Oh, right, brother

428
00:30:57,160 --> 00:30:58,839
Who were you just on the phone with?

429
00:31:00,640 --> 00:31:01,240
No one

430
00:31:01,240 --> 00:31:03,079
I clearly heard you talking to someone

431
00:31:03,440 --> 00:31:04,720
Let me see your call history

432
00:31:09,599 --> 00:31:11,839
I'm going to check the fabric I dyed yesterday.

433
00:31:12,519 --> 00:31:13,359
Bro,

434
00:31:14,880 --> 00:31:16,200
Everyone get up now!

435
00:31:17,279 --> 00:31:18,559
Hurry up and pick up the ball!

436
00:31:20,359 --> 00:31:22,039
Are you waiting for me to feed it to you?

437
00:31:22,440 --> 00:31:23,640
Every single one of you,

438
00:31:23,880 --> 00:31:25,079
how soft have you become?

439
00:31:25,680 --> 00:31:26,720
I want athletes,

440
00:31:26,720 --> 00:31:27,759
not male models.

441
00:31:27,880 --> 00:31:29,480
Should I get a nanny to coddle you?

442
00:31:29,759 --> 00:31:30,759
Brother Yu,

443
00:31:30,759 --> 00:31:32,279
How about we take a day off?

444
00:31:32,480 --> 00:31:33,359
Are you crazy?

445
00:31:33,359 --> 00:31:34,400
Talking to him about taking a break?

446
00:31:34,400 --> 00:31:35,160
I'll train you to death.

447
00:31:40,519 --> 00:31:41,359
What's the date tomorrow?

448
00:31:41,839 --> 00:31:42,720
The 7th.

449
00:31:45,200 --> 00:31:45,880
Okay.

450
00:31:46,039 --> 00:31:46,480
Let's take a day off.

451
00:31:46,480 --> 00:31:47,319
Brother Qiu Yu,

452
00:31:48,400 --> 00:31:50,119
Director Wang asked me to tell you

453
00:31:50,400 --> 00:31:51,480
that tomorrow

454
00:31:51,920 --> 00:31:53,920
ten Team Doctors will come for interviews.

455
00:31:56,519 --> 00:31:57,559
Of that caliber,

456
00:31:58,480 --> 00:31:59,799
he'll decide for himself.

457
00:32:00,799 --> 00:32:01,680
I have something tomorrow.

458
00:32:09,240 --> 00:32:10,200
I'm busy.

459
00:32:13,680 --> 00:32:14,440
What did he say?

460
00:32:14,759 --> 00:32:16,200
He said he's busy tomorrow.

461
00:32:16,200 --> 00:32:16,960
Busy?

462
00:32:17,880 --> 00:32:18,440
No.

463
00:32:18,640 --> 00:32:20,240
What could be more important than this?

464
00:32:32,480 --> 00:32:33,279
Let's go, Gu Hao.

465
00:32:33,279 --> 00:32:34,400
Let's go get some barbecue.

466
00:32:35,079 --> 00:32:36,440
Who wants to go join the fun with you?

467
00:32:36,920 --> 00:32:38,240
Someone's coming to pick me up.

468
00:32:41,559 --> 00:32:42,359
Zhou Song.

469
00:32:51,279 --> 00:32:52,000
Get in.

470
00:33:12,279 --> 00:33:13,759
The one who put his arm around you just now

471
00:33:14,160 --> 00:33:14,920
What did he want?

472
00:33:15,960 --> 00:33:17,640
He wanted to ask me out to dinner to celebrate.

473
00:33:17,880 --> 00:33:19,359
He said his swing speed

474
00:33:19,480 --> 00:33:20,640
is catching up to Qiu Yu Ge.

475
00:33:20,640 --> 00:33:21,359
Really?

476
00:33:25,680 --> 00:33:26,480
Let him catch up.

477
00:33:27,079 --> 00:33:29,079
He'll break his legs trying and still won't catch up.

478
00:33:30,079 --> 00:33:31,079
That's true.

479
00:33:31,559 --> 00:33:33,119
This celebration dinner is too early.

480
00:33:34,680 --> 00:33:36,759
That's the only downside to Old Zhai's club:

481
00:33:37,200 --> 00:33:38,440
It's full of rough guys.

482
00:33:38,440 --> 00:33:39,200
So boring.

483
00:33:42,960 --> 00:33:44,720
Are you really not considering my job offer?

484
00:33:48,400 --> 00:33:49,160
No way.

485
00:33:52,240 --> 00:33:54,319
Who knows what they'd make me do if I went.

486
00:34:01,079 --> 00:34:02,880
I wonder how Li Youen is doing lately.

487
00:34:03,079 --> 00:34:04,000
He's doing great.

488
00:34:04,319 --> 00:34:05,880
His uncle is immigrating soon.

489
00:34:06,119 --> 00:34:07,319
He's thinking about whether to sell the shop

490
00:34:07,319 --> 00:34:08,280
at a low price to them.

491
00:34:08,280 --> 00:34:09,239
How do you know all this?

492
00:34:10,000 --> 00:34:11,320
Li Yousisi told me.

493
00:34:11,559 --> 00:34:12,480
Youen's younger sister.

494
00:34:14,559 --> 00:34:15,960
How did you start talking to him again?

495
00:34:17,000 --> 00:34:18,159
Why do you have so many friends?

496
00:34:19,440 --> 00:34:20,760
We're about the same age.

497
00:34:20,760 --> 00:34:21,559
We get along well.

498
00:34:34,400 --> 00:34:35,480
You're going the wrong way.

499
00:34:35,599 --> 00:34:36,719
My home is that way.

500
00:34:36,960 --> 00:34:38,400
You're not going home tonight.

501
00:34:52,840 --> 00:34:54,440
I said I'm off today.

502
00:34:54,440 --> 00:34:55,639
Is that so hard to understand?

503
00:34:56,360 --> 00:34:57,639
Don't you always work?

504
00:34:58,559 --> 00:34:59,559
That was before.

505
00:35:00,159 --> 00:35:01,920
Someone needs me to rest now.

506
00:35:02,239 --> 00:35:03,400
I have to rest.

507
00:35:03,400 --> 00:35:05,400
But the Team Doctors are all waiting here.

508
00:35:06,239 --> 00:35:08,079
Didn't Gu Hao make it clear to you yesterday?

509
00:35:08,599 --> 00:35:10,840
With that kind of quality, it's the same for anyone.

510
00:35:20,320 --> 00:35:21,559
How do I do it?

511
00:35:27,119 --> 00:35:29,079
This binding has to be tied securely.

512
00:35:29,360 --> 00:35:29,800
Otherwise,

513
00:35:29,800 --> 00:35:32,320
it'll fall apart easily when it's floating.

514
00:35:32,639 --> 00:35:33,679
It'll be ruined.

515
00:35:35,480 --> 00:35:36,679
I'm not always at the shop,

516
00:35:37,079 --> 00:35:38,960
and I can't always watch you do this.

517
00:35:38,960 --> 00:35:39,880
I know.

518
00:35:40,760 --> 00:35:42,239
Then I'll have to learn slowly.

519
00:35:42,880 --> 00:35:44,519
If you really learn it,

520
00:35:44,519 --> 00:35:46,199
then about Uncle's offer to take over the shop,

521
00:35:46,199 --> 00:35:47,480
we'll really have to consider it.

522
00:35:50,480 --> 00:35:51,159
Look

523
00:35:51,920 --> 00:35:52,559
Like this

524
00:35:56,519 --> 00:35:57,440
Brother

525
00:36:02,920 --> 00:36:03,960
This is so hard

526
00:36:05,920 --> 00:36:06,880
It's okay

527
00:36:07,360 --> 00:36:08,119
Just learn slowly

528
00:36:09,320 --> 00:36:09,880
Mm

529
00:36:14,320 --> 00:36:15,039
Li Youen

530
00:36:35,360 --> 00:36:36,360
He's moving

531
00:36:38,199 --> 00:36:39,159
Just to avoid me

532
00:36:43,280 --> 00:36:44,119
No way!

533
00:36:44,760 --> 00:36:45,960
I'm going to hide his luggage.

534
00:37:05,159 --> 00:37:06,280
What are you doing?

535
00:37:12,039 --> 00:37:13,760
Weren't we doing fine these past two days?

536
00:37:15,280 --> 00:37:16,679
Why are you trying to abandon me again?

537
00:37:17,800 --> 00:37:18,800
What are you talking about?

538
00:37:21,360 --> 00:37:22,480
I didn't do anything wrong.

539
00:37:23,159 --> 00:37:24,280
Even if I did something wrong,

540
00:37:24,639 --> 00:37:25,400
just tell me.

541
00:37:25,639 --> 00:37:26,679
I'll fix it, okay?

542
00:37:27,559 --> 00:37:28,639
And you said

543
00:37:28,880 --> 00:37:29,960
you'd give me a chance.

544
00:37:30,400 --> 00:37:31,760
But after I went back to the club,

545
00:37:32,480 --> 00:37:33,440
you changed your mind.

546
00:37:34,639 --> 00:37:35,400
Give me the suitcase.

547
00:37:35,400 --> 00:37:36,960
If I don't leave now, I'll miss my train.

548
00:37:36,960 --> 00:37:37,679
No.

549
00:37:42,480 --> 00:37:43,920
I've already booked the car.

550
00:37:44,159 --> 00:37:45,199
I've already paid the money.

551
00:37:45,559 --> 00:37:46,400
How much?

552
00:37:46,400 --> 00:37:47,039
I'll pay him double.

553
00:37:47,519 --> 00:37:48,559
I'll pay him ten times over.

554
00:37:53,840 --> 00:37:54,599
Or

555
00:37:55,960 --> 00:37:56,880
Where are you going?

556
00:37:57,719 --> 00:37:58,800
Give me the address.

557
00:37:59,280 --> 00:37:59,920
I'll take you.

558
00:38:00,519 --> 00:38:01,440
My car is right outside.

559
00:38:10,840 --> 00:38:11,480
The address

560
00:38:12,360 --> 00:38:12,960
Let's go.

561
00:38:14,559 --> 00:38:15,000
Top

562
00:38:15,360 --> 00:38:16,199
The top floor

563
00:38:19,440 --> 00:38:20,159
My place

564
00:38:21,519 --> 00:38:23,440
I want to move somewhere closer

565
00:38:23,800 --> 00:38:25,760
So you don't have to run back and forth every weekend

566
00:38:26,000 --> 00:38:27,320
You'll get exhausted and still have to pay me.

567
00:38:30,719 --> 00:38:31,360
Not tired.

568
00:38:31,800 --> 00:38:32,719
Not tired at all.

569
00:38:33,159 --> 00:38:33,840
Youen.

570
00:38:35,960 --> 00:38:36,920
Besides,

571
00:38:37,199 --> 00:38:38,840
I've been keeping an eye on your injury.

572
00:38:38,840 --> 00:38:40,360
I wouldn't feel at ease leaving it to someone else.

573
00:38:41,599 --> 00:38:42,360
Yeah.

574
00:38:42,880 --> 00:38:44,719
How could you possibly feel at ease leaving me to someone else?

575
00:38:45,719 --> 00:38:46,639
Zhai Qiuyu.

576
00:38:47,360 --> 00:38:48,920
Don't always copy what I say.
